    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Occultist Sacred Implement</strong><br/><br/><p><b>Deity </b>Pharasma; <b>Implement </b>brooch; <b>Opposition School </b>abjuration</p><p><i>Grandmother's Ward (Su): </i>As a standard action, you can expend 3 points of psychic focus to create a 5-foot-radius ward centered on you for 1 round per occultist level. This ward burns undead creatures, dealing an amount of damage equal to 1d4 + 1d4 per 2 occultist levels you have when the undead enter the ward and each round they begin their turns within this area of effect. The warded area moves with you and can be used only defensively. Any attempt to force the ward against an undead creature immediately ends the effect.</p>",
